    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this function is low. Scalar functions that perform straightforward data type conversions or formatting typically involve simple logic and minimal computational overhead. The function likely uses built-in SQL Server functions to achieve the conversion, which are optimized for performance."
        }
