      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function accepts one or more input parameters, with the primary parameter being a date or datetime value. This parameter serves as the input date that the function will convert into a string format. Additional parameters, if any, might specify the desired format for the output string or handle locale-specific formatting requirements."
        }
