          "type": "text",
          "text": "The return type of the function is a string (VARCHAR or NVARCHAR). This string represents the formatted date, converted from the input date value. The specific length of the string type (e.g., VARCHAR(10), NVARCHAR(20)) depends on the expected format of the output date string."
